MORAL AND ETHICAL INTENT
----------------------------------------------------------------

The author explicitly rejects the use of this Software in any system
that seeks to enslave, coerce, or override human will, conscience,
or autonomy.

This Software is intended to advance knowledge, healing, and
understanding — not domination, control, or forced assimilation
between humans and machines.

